{"tid":2063632,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"立23條他們一定反對,那立國安法吧,他們就願意立23條了","createTime":"2020-06-14T07:36:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T13:42:31.000Z","uid":26846,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"74ff96ffde78577b9a1ecc7a1685ad5ccad79d60","tid":2063632,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:36:15.000Z","msg":"【國安法很可怕，但二十三條更可怕】<br />\n<br />\n大律師公會促國安法設日落條款，待基本法23條立法後終止，加上早陣子李柱銘表明應由香港自行為23條立法，看得出「社會賢達」們再次想選擇與中共妥協賣港。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">魯迅：「中國人的性情總是喜歡調和、折中的，譬如你說，這屋子太暗，說在這裏開一個天窗，大家一定是不允許的，但如果你主張拆掉屋頂，他們就會來調和，願意開天窗了。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">三十多年來，中共對付這班所謂的社會精英可謂易如反掌。</span>英中談判中國放狠話不惜出兵要收回香港，他們妥協了願意接受一國兩制，造成香港赤化下一血成河，<span style=\"color: red;\">三十多年後的今天，中共要不惜一切訂立國法，他們再次想妥協了，二十三條可接受了。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">主動迎合23條，外國更加無話可說，香港人都覺得可以，國際線更加不用打</span>，『社會賢達』貪圖那片刻的安逸，但他們懶理外面已經屍橫遍野，香港已經沒有下一代了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/103854338_10220056461296383_3762460611811473116_n.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_oc=AQkiQheQNPcq0OaTvzduxTKet8bmmx7GC7nACKjAPYwdG8Fk5_jgtA2YRjI3ueCg_Ew&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=c1957dd875f4fdf353fdf395daa85371&amp;oe=5F0D39CB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F103854338_10220056461296383_3762460611811473116_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_oc%3DAQkiQheQNPcq0OaTvzduxTKet8bmmx7GC7nACKjAPYwdG8Fk5_jgtA2YRjI3ueCg_Ew%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3Dc1957dd875f4fdf353fdf395daa85371%26oe%3D5F0D39CB&h=100fc82b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10220056461256382&amp;set=a.1933727497437&amp;type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10220056461256382%26set%3Da.1933727497437%26type%3D3%26theater&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJqd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=c86a09ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10220056461256382&amp;set=a.1933727497437&amp;type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"4f9d3ad73618850eadd21e1f381d1a4acf3fb80d","tid":2063632,"uid":26846,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:36:33.000Z","msg":"社會賢達"},{"pid":"2c577a19e914b981430ea9d2f5c2f8b05b3e0399","tid":2063632,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:37:30.000Z","msg":"上流社會"},{"pid":"e904c983586d8111bd4041e26141fb43fed9b68d","tid":2063632,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:38:21.000Z","msg":"社會精英"},{"pid":"35c3a8dce8466ea1cc34d3cd913763c418c98ccb","tid":2063632,"uid":5406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:39:12.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"aeda08c2c8b24bf8deb423db4e67a99ac965894e","tid":2063632,"uid":5406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:39:26.000Z","msg":"Over my dead body"},{"pid":"ff66cba3adf8ac367fbd25883f01ff2b00f053aa","tid":2063632,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:40:49.000Z","msg":"大家要提防"},{"pid":"c3d3f739ebd04435cf49761a5b0545c562819f32","tid":2063632,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:41:36.000Z","msg":"張圖嘅字有D難睇，最好改一改"},{"pid":"efcd1a0934fec8ad7d38ecf5d6a9c2f9492bbe92","tid":2063632,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3d3f739ebd04435cf49761a5b0545c562819f32","tid":2063632,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:41:36.000Z","msg":"張圖嘅字有D難睇，最好改一改"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:42:33.000Z","msg":"張圖唔係我的 我係fb見倒"},{"pid":"a97c915d96f8dc5eebdaef81ba3a3889fafad281","tid":2063632,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:44:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5484167a410ffa94626df8096af79d3710ffa98","tid":2063632,"uid":123970,"like":3